/* MEMBER NAME:     FORMATHA                                               */
/* FUNCTION RETURN TYPE:                                                   */
/*          CHARACTER                                                      */
/* INPUT PARAMETERS:                                                       */
/*          HALMAT#           BIT(16)                                      */
/* LOCAL DECLARATIONS:                                                     */
/*          HALMAT_PRINT#     BIT(16)                                      */
/*          BLOCK#            BIT(16)                                      */
/*          MESSAGE           CHARACTER;                                   */
/* EXTERNAL VARIABLES REFERENCED:                                          */
/*          ASTERISK                                                       */
/*          BLANK                                                          */
/*          BLOCK_PRIME                                                    */
/*          CLOSE                                                          */
/*          COLON                                                          */
/*          COMMA                                                          */
/*          CURR_HALMAT_BLOCK                                              */
/*          HALMAT_SIZE                                                    */
/*          HALMAT                                                         */
/*          LEFT_PAREN                                                     */
/*          PERIOD                                                         */
/*          RIGHT_PAREN                                                    */
/* EXTERNAL VARIABLES CHANGED:                                             */
/*          TEMP_MAT                                                       */
/* EXTERNAL PROCEDURES CALLED:                                             */
/*          #RJUST                                                         */
/*          HEX                                                            */
